## What this gives you

```text
Frontend project:
MediaUpload.razor
    - MudBlazor UI
    - file selector
    - parallel upload selector
    - chunk size selector
    - progress bars

mediaChunkUploader.js
    - splits files into chunks
    - uploads chunks in parallel
    - calls backend controller endpoints
```

Change this value for 4, 5, or 6 parallel chunk uploads:

```csharp
private int _parallelUploadLimit = 4;
```

And this is the backend URL:

```csharp
backendBaseUrl = "https://localhost:7001"
```

Change it to your backend API project URL.
